   Investors Home      News      Events & Presentations      Financial Reporting      Quarterly Results      SEC Filings      Annual Reports        Corporate Governance      Governance Documents      Committee Composition      Board of Directors      Management        Stock Information      Investor Resources      FAQ      Analyst Coverage          Media      Media Home      Hilton News      Our Brands      Media Kit      Resources      Awards                             Hilton is one of the largest hospitality companies in the world, with nearly 5,000 properties with more than 812,000 rooms in 103 countries and territories. Hilton is one of the largest hospitality companies in the world, with nearly 5,000 properties with more than 812,000 rooms in 103 countries and territories. In the nearly 100 years since our founding, we have defined the hospitality industry and established a portfolio of 14 world-class brands, including our flagship Hilton Hotels & Resorts brand, which is the most recognized hotel brand in the world. Our premier brand portfolio also includes Waldorf Astoria Hotels & Resorts, Conrad Hotels & Resorts, Canopy by Hilton, Curio Collection by Hilton, Tapestry Collection by Hilton, DoubleTree by Hilton, Embassy Suites by Hilton, Hilton Garden Inn, Hampton by Hilton, Tru by Hilton, Homewood Suites by Hilton, Home2 Suites by Hilton and Hilton Grand Vacations. We have more than 62 million members in our award–winning customer loyalty program, Hilton Honors.        History & Heritage     Conrad N. Hilton began with a 40-room hotel in a small Texas town in 1919. Today, Hilton is the world's preeminent hospitality company, stretching across 24 time zones. You'll find us in world capitals, rural roadsides, trade centers, vacation destinations, and everywhere in between. Learn more about how we got here – and where we intend to go next.  Learn about our history & heritage       Executive Committee     With experience in hospitality and related industries, our executive team is well-positioned to accelerate our global momentum.  Christopher J. Nassetta, President & Chief Executive Officer View full executive team    Vision, Mission, and Values     Our vision is to fill the earth with the light and warmth of hospitality, by being the first choice of hotel guests, team members, and owners alike.  Learn about our vision, mission, and values        At a Glance    Download the latest factsheet                        Skip to top of page            Waldorf Astoria Collection   Offers unforgettable experiences at iconic destinations around the world.        Conrad Hotels & Resorts   Offers smart luxury travelers inspiring connections and intuitive service in a world of style.      Conrad Hotels & Resorts   Offers smart luxury travelers inspiring connections and intuitive service in a world of style.      Conrad Hotels & Resorts   Offers smart luxury travelers inspiring connections and intuitive service in a world of style.      Conrad Hotels & Resorts   Offers smart luxury travelers inspiring connections and intuitive service in a world of style.      Conrad Hotels & Resorts   Offers smart luxury travelers inspiring connections and intuitive service in a world of style.      Conrad Hotels & Resorts   Offers smart luxury travelers inspiring connections and intuitive service in a world of style.      Conrad Hotels & Resorts   Offers smart luxury travelers inspiring connections and intuitive service in a world of style.      Conrad Hotels & Resorts   Offers smart luxury travelers inspiring connections and intuitive service in a world of style.      Conrad Hotels & Resorts   Offers smart luxury travelers inspiring connections and intuitive service in a world of style.      Conrad Hotels & Resorts   Offers smart luxury travelers inspiring connections and intuitive service in a world of style.      Conrad Hotels & Resorts   Offers smart luxury travelers inspiring connections and intuitive service in a world of style.      Conrad Hotel