With more than 550 hotels & resorts on six continents, Hilton remains the most recognized hotel brand.
A collection of hotels that gives you the peace of mind to travel independently.
Discover a group of unique and extraordinary hotels inspired by New York’s legend.
The contemporary luxury brand of Hilton Hotels.
Canopy is the fresh, neighborhood hotel that delivers a positive stay.
A collection of unique hotels appealing to travelers seeking local discovery.
Warm. Comfortable. Friendly. We provide true comfort to today’s business and leisure travelers.
Relaxed, upscale environment with over 200 all-suite locations in the US, Canada and Latin America.
Sleep Deep, Work Smart, Eat Well, Stay Fit and Treat Yourself with every stay.
Trusted for a good night’s rest by value conscious and quality minded travelers.
Whether you’re staying two days or two weeks, we’ve got everything you need to Be at home.
Comfy, stylish and packed with perks for the value conscious, extended stay traveler.
Enjoy the benefits of your very own vacation villa, without the hassles of second home ownership.
HHonors is the Loyalty Program for all Hilton properties. 
A revolutionary new brand that is simplified, spirited and grounded in value for guests with a zest for life and a desire for human connection. 
























